        "subject": "LU-12058 tests: skip sanity 51d if stripe offset is unsuited",
        "message": "LU-12058 tests: skip sanity 51d if stripe offset is unsuited\n\nsanity.sh:test_51d needs stripe offset to be -1 so that round robin\nalgorithm was used to select an OST for a first stripe. If stripe\noffset is not -1 the test fails.\n\nCheck that root and working directories both have stripe offset set to\n-1 and skip the test if they are not.\n\nCray-bug-id: LUS-7097\nSigned-off-by: Vladimir Saveliev <c17830@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I22f68edff66a65c8b8eeb3917b90c8b60f413638\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
